            <title>[SPARK-6286] Handle TASK_ERROR in TaskState</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-6286</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Scala warning:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;match may not be exhaustive. It would fail on the following input: TASK_ERROR
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
